Traveling with more than one passport in your pocket always comes with a spy thriller novel-like allure.
A dual or triple citizen needs to make sure their movements don’t peeve the authorities of the countries they visit.
He estimates that up to 80% of the firm’s clientele are seeking a second passport in order to get visa-free access to a broader range of countries.
“What always surprises me is how few of our clients actually ask the question: How do I use this now that I have it?
I would say probably only 10% of our clients actually [ask that].”